  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Duty Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide support to the Lounge Manager with operational tasks and responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Responsible for managing the front of house operations to ensure we are providing the high-quality service to our customers.</li>\n  <li>Supervision and support of all lounge areas as required</li>\n  <li>Lead by example to provide efficient, friendly &amp; professional food &amp; beverage service to all guests by ensuring a high level of customer service.</li>\n  <li>Assist in assigning duties and ensure that suitable staff levels are maintained. Assist in daily team briefings when needed.</li>\n  <li>Apply knowledge and empowerment to resolve all lounge issues.</li>\n  <li>Complete incident and injury reports on site.</li>\n  <li>Assist in handling different guest challenges and situations and be part of the first response emergency team.</li>\n  <li>Assisting with training/onboarding of new team members.</li>\n  <li>Maintain standards of hygiene for food handling and presentation as prescribed by council / legislative regulations, in accordance with the Lounges and Qantas Food Safety Plan.</li>\n  <li>Show efficiency in constantly striving to provide total customer satisfaction.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 2-3 years of related experience as Senior Lounge Host and (or) Assistant Duty Manager; or Restaurant / Outlet Manager in a similar set-up and capacity</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and problem solving skills</li>\n  <li>Ability to manage team members in a calm and respectful manner</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal skill especially in handling customer feedback</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Work Location:</strong></p>\n<p>Changi Airport</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested and qualifies candidates are to submit their application with a detailed resume.</p>",
