    "description": "<p>Accor Hotels (AAPC Services Pte Ltd) operates and manages the Qantas Singapore Lounges and we have exciting opportunities for you to join us!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Based at Singapore Changi Airport Terminal 1, the Qantas Singapore Lounges offers a new standard of luxury for our guests travelling through Singapore. The lounge reflects the heart of Singapore, a vibrant and exciting space that celebrates the heritage scene.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>As a key member of our team, you will represent our friendly and professional service philosophy of Feel Valued and Feel Welcome.</p>",
